                    "line_length": "5",
                    "rhyme": "3"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Triste à ma cellule,\nQuand la nuit s'abat,\nJe n'ai de pendule\nQue mon cœur qui bat :\nSi l'ombre changeante\nNoircit mon séjour,\nQuelque atome chante,\nQui m'apprend le jour."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 2,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 9,
                    "line_text": "Dans ma cheminée,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "5",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 10,
                    "line_text": "Un grillon fervent,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "5",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 11,
                    "line_text": "Faisant sa tournée,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "5",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 12,
                    "line_text": "Jette un cri vivant :",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "5",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 13,
                    "line_text": "C'est à moi qu'il livre",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "5",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
