                    "line_text": "Et d'être grillon !",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "5",
                    "rhyme": "d"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Dans ma cheminée,\nUn grillon fervent,\nFaisant sa tournée,\nJette un cri vivant :\nC'est à moi qu'il livre\nSon fin carillon,\nTout charmé de vivre\nEt d'être grillon !"
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 3,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 17,
                    "line_text": "La bonté du Maître",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "5",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 18,
                    "line_text": "Se glisse en tout lieu ;",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "5",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 19,
                    "line_text": "Son plus petit être",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "5",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 20,
                    "line_text": "Fait songer à Dieu.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "5",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 21,
                    "line_text": "Sait-il qu'on l'envie,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "5",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 22,
                    "line_text": "Seul et ténébreux :",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "5",
                    "rhyme": "d"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 23,
                    "line_text": "Il aime la vie ;",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "5",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 24,
                    "line_text": "Il est bien heureux !",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "5",
                    "rhyme": "d"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "La bonté du Maître\nSe glisse en tout lieu ;\nSon plus petit être\nFait songer à Dieu.\nSait-il qu'on l'envie,\nSeul et ténébreux :\nIl aime la vie ;\nIl est bien heureux !"
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 4,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 25,
                    "line_text": "La guerre enfiévrée",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "5",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 26,
                    "line_text": "Passait l'autrefois,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "5",
                    "rhyme": "b"
