                    "line_text": "Je chauffe ses jours ;",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "5",
                    "rhyme": "d"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 39,
                    "line_text": "Mais, femme, je pleure :",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "5",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 40,
                    "line_text": "Lui, chante toujours.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "5",
                    "rhyme": "d"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Dieu nous fit, me semble,\nQuelque parité :\nAu même âtre ensemble\nNous avons chanté ;\nIl me frappe l'heure,\nJe chauffe ses jours ;\nMais, femme, je pleure :\nLui, chante toujours."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 6,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 41,
                    "line_text": "Si jamais la fée",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "5",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 42,
                    "line_text": "Au soulier d'azur,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "5",
                    "rhyme": "b"
